{"tid":2224398,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反鑑證 反追蹤】網絡安全專業教學","createTime":"2020-09-30T12:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T17:58:59.000Z","uid":110079,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"552c8881780632dfdb776e2de7cacc6f1128b871","tid":2224398,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:43:58.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\"><strong>開始前，請知道自己嘅網絡安全知識有幾多，如果係新手嘅話，呢度未必適合你，你可以去上周庭嘅網絡安全bb班先。</strong></span></span> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V7u9LxjJDtg&amp;ab_channel=%E5%91%A8%E5%BA%AD%E3%83%81%E3%83%A3%E3%83%B3%E3%83%8D%E3%83%AB \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DV7u9LxjJDtg%26ab_channel%3D%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E3%2583%2581%25E3%2583%25A3%25E3%2583%25B3%25E3%2583%258D%25E3%2583%25AB%20&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyh5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=7f86d5f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V7u9LxjJDtg&amp;ab_channel=%E5%91%A8%E5%BA%AD%E3%83%81%E3%83%A3%E3%83%B3%E3%83%8D%E3%83%AB </a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>呢個攻略係純教學，較少解釋術語同原理 。如果你唔明，可以上網search如果有嘅自己上網search了解更多。 </strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>網絡安全（Cyber Security）</strong>分為兩大類，分別係<span class=\"red\"><strong>反電子鑑證(Anti-forensics)</strong></span>以及<span class=\"red\"><strong>反電子追蹤(Anti-tracking) </strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n進行呢兩種措施前，硬件亦有要求，就係要<strong>鬼機鬼卡</strong>。<br />\n<strong>手機要求：</strong><br />\na) 最好<span class=\"blue\">新機同較新型號</span>(新機較難被破解，建議買pixel／iphone，而其他encrypted phone喺香港好難買到)，買嘅時候都唔好check location／開wifi connection) 。二手機就盡量揀非本地用過嘅<br />\nb) 有一定電子安全知識嘅 可選<span class=\"blue\">linux/android系統電話</span>，因為更高嘅私隱調整自由度<br />\n<br />\n<strong>太空卡：</strong>無特別要求，只要非大陸供應商就ok<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">反鑑證(Anti-forensic)</span></span><br />\n電話鑑證大致上分為三種方法:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yu5gZoo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYu5gZoo.png&h=d7e76fc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三個方法當中，logical acquisition係最容易，消耗時間較短。相反如果鑑證人員需要拎最全面嘅數據，可能就要利用physical acqu。 不過相當耗時間且有機會破壞原有檔案 。<br />\n<br />\n最原始亦能保護數據嘅最好鑑證方法係成功破解密碼（所以<span class=\"blue\">密碼係最重要嘅保壘之一</span>）。現時知名鑑證儀器供應商有<strong><span class=\"blue\">Cellebrite</span></strong>同<strong><span class=\"blue\">Grayshift</span></strong>。<br />\n<strong>要點防止數據洩露嘅教學如下</strong>：<br />\n<strong>1. 基本手機設定</strong><br />\n- 新增<span class=\"red\">sim lock</span>同數據<span class=\"red\">資料加密(data encryption)</span>。<br />\n- 取消所有app位置(location)權限，Apps有得<span class=\"red\">2FA/2SV</span>嘅就開。<br />\n- disable 所有icloud/Google backup，location，bluetooth<br />\n- disable所有google app，andriod改用<span class=\"blue\">F-driod下載FOSS軟件</span>，就算需要用到google play／App store都用假帳下載<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 備份(Backup)</strong><br />\n推薦用<strong><span class=\"red\">外置儲存器（eg. usb）&gt;雲端儲存</span></strong><br />\n外置儲存器: <span class=\"blue\">SecureDrive</span><span class=\"blue\">(軍用級加密硬碟</span>，相當貴) ，或者普通usb + software加密（e.g. <span class=\"blue\">symantec endpoint encryption, TrueCrypt</span>）<br />\n棄用Google Drive, 改用Nextcloud / TeamDrive<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>3. 文件加密(File encryption) &amp; 文件匿藏法(File Concealment)</strong></span><br />\n電腦: <span class=\"blue\">Veracrypt</span>同<span class=\"blue\">AES crypt</span>可以創建<strong>虛擬加密磁盤文件</strong>，利用演算法增加密碼複雜性破解難度。呢個方法適合儲存一啲重要並且要keep住嘅資料。<br />\nveracrypt仲有得創建<span class=\"blue\">隱藏式磁盤文件</span>。<br />\n中文教學：<a href=\"https://izaka.tw/2015-3-8-226/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fizaka.tw%2F2015-3-8-226%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyh5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=ebb532ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://izaka.tw/2015-3-8-226/</a><br />\nEnglish version: <a href=\"https://proprivacy.com/privacy-service/guides/veracrypt-how-to-basics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fproprivacy.com%2Fprivacy-service%2Fguides%2Fveracrypt-how-to-basics&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyh5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=426e60d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://proprivacy.com/privacy-service/guides/veracrypt-how-to-basics</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Andriod:</strong>下載<span class=\"blue\"><strong>SSE</strong></span>，將重要檔案加密隱藏。<span class=\"blue\">去app --&gt; 禁File/Dir Encryptor --&gt;揀檔案 --&gt;Encrypt file --&gt;set密碼</span>。需要用時就解密（decrypt）。<br />\n<strong>iOS</strong>: 用<span class=\"blue\">securesafe／cryptomator</span>（收費），但iphone本身有內置file加密，所以並唔大問題。<br />\n<br />\n其他方法例如:data steganography(數據隱寫術) ，但個人認為以上兩種已經足夠，所以唔晒篇幅寫。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">4. 數據刪除(data wipe) / 數據覆寫(data overwriting)</span></strong><br />\n真正<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>永久刪除資料</strong></span>方法係多次覆寫原有數據儲存空間。定期要<span class=\"blue\">清除cache+做overwriting</span>。<br />\n<strong>Apps</strong>： <span class=\"blue\">ishredder</span> (Andriod版免費，有<strong>軍用級數據銷毀</strong>選擇)<br />\n<em>ps: Protectstar 有各種反間諜安全程式提供（部分需要收費) 。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.protectstar.com/en/for-android\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.protectstar.com%2Fen%2Ffor-android&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyh5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=2e1b689a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.protectstar.com/en/for-android</a></em><br />\n<br />\n<strong>5. 鍵盤輸入</strong><br />\n電話會<span class=\"blue\">儲存文字輸入歷史</span>，入侵者可以借呢個漏洞去盜取密碼等重要資訊。清除方法<br />\n<strong>Andriod:</strong> 去設定--&gt;一般管理--&gt;語言及輸入--&gt;螢幕鍵盤，揀用緊嘅鍵盤--&gt;重置為預設設定&amp;取消personalized serivce<br />\n<strong>iOS: </strong>去設定--&gt;一般重設--&gt;重設鍵盤辭典<br />\n或者簡單啲就去設定--&gt;應用程式--&gt;揀第三方鍵盤App，然後<span class=\"blue\">clear data&amp;cache</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://windowsreport.com/anti-keylogger-software/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwindowsreport.com%2Fanti-keylogger-software%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyh5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=7e6abab9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://windowsreport.com/anti-keylogger-software/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>6. Metadata</strong><br />\n好多電話相機相片會有metadata，可能<span class=\"blue\">透露相片拍攝位址同手機硬件資料</span>，所以係share出去嘅時候要remove咗先。 <br />\n<strong>Andriod</strong>:下載<span class=\"blue\">Scrambled Exif</span>，喺share相之前揀呢個先（禁落相share就有呢個選擇）<br />\n<strong>iOS</strong>: Metapho<strong><br />\n電腦</strong>：除咗<span class=\"blue\">去terminal改metadata</span>，可以去 <a href=\"https://www.verexif.com/en/改。如果想匿名上載文件，可以下載\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.verexif.com%2Fen%2F%E6%94%B9%E3%80%82%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E6%83%B3%E5%8C%BF%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%8A%E8%BC%89%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E8%BC%89&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyh5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=60ffcd37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.verexif.com/en/改。如果想匿名上載文件，可以下載</a><span class=\"blue\">onionshare</span>透過tor去share<br />\n<br />\n另一個做法<strong>係screenshot將相先send（電話／電腦）</strong><br />\n<br />\n至於平時用開嘅文件editor（eg microsoft word）Metadata，去返word<span class=\"blue\">揀Review--&gt;Protect--&gt;Protect document--&gt;揀&quot;remove personal info from this file on save&quot;同set密碼</span><br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>pdf清除metadata方法</strong>：去pdf properties改。但簡單起見，直接去<a href=\"https://www.pdfyeah.com/remove-pdf-metadata/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pdfyeah.com%2Fremove-pdf-metadata%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyh5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=47fef0e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pdfyeah.com/remove-pdf-metadata/</a>"},{"pid":"3b42a6327a25917f8eb80aeb06c49c09adbcae85","tid":2224398,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:46:34.000Z","msg":"不段出現未明問題 po唔到"},{"pid":"fcb53d8fc7479700dae108631d57c4eff37df87b","tid":2224398,"uid":91272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b42a6327a25917f8eb80aeb06c49c09adbcae85","tid":2224398,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:46:34.000Z","msg":"不段出現未明問題 po唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa20a6335b72cd66bb0cd1b294e290050cb47aa","tid":2224398,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:47:52.000Z","msg":"<strong>7. 防毒軟件(Antivirus software)</strong><br />\n每部機都有<strong>內置防毒軟件</strong>，但如果想有更好保護，包括防止keylogger、rootkits、木馬、間諜malware，可以下載<span class=\"blue\"><strong>Bitdefender(推薦)/ malwarebytes / Kaspersky / Norton</strong></span>。<br />\n<em>ps: 各軟件有優弱點，雖然暫時共用並無發現有software crash，但一款其實都足夠。</em>"},{"pid":"c2b3712788d47d8b9b57117d0709e814e6b20902","tid":2224398,"uid":199766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:51:35.000Z","msg":"高汁post"},{"pid":"37a41beebc7474e81ed510baaa21499068ad031b","tid":2224398,"uid":199766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:51:45.000Z","msg":"冇理由唔推"},{"pid":"c7c603a4c0c2f92be94981e0eaebc19c46b0fc54","tid":2224398,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:52:21.000Z","msg":"唔po了 不斷出未知問題唔比回覆 有冇連仔知道發生咩問題"},{"pid":"3cfda002b9caa4bfcaf0865f15132ac9e5f83ee4","tid":2224398,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:52:53.000Z","msg":"sor個app有問題 再po過"},{"pid":"76e85e3994c616997d54e52c0a936e752b6b9497","tid":2224398,"uid":304435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:55:59.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17ed55f371aea9d2e21f879af82dc21ac2806a7e","tid":2224398,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T13:02:30.000Z","msg":"做足哂有幾多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c1324bcaae772e9f3f009409415f974fbf6811","tid":2224398,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T13:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37418d76321e7c43096819a4343a3becf7a053fa","tid":2224398,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T13:18:29.000Z","msg":"暫時唔po了 一長文回覆就出問題po唔到..."},{"pid":"014df8f3a7475e8bd95f00b95376360e715049e5","tid":2224398,"uid":179126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T16:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d0944ca07a762b51b4b7336e783795c35f4c0d8","tid":2224398,"uid":54622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T16:07:54.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"a4b0224bd26d6c2dc74212261a8bec209f13bbf3","tid":2224398,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T16:26:59.000Z","msg":"唔錯既post<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096295af3713aeb264adb31f12718af3a6bc2544","tid":2224398,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"552c8881780632dfdb776e2de7cacc6f1128b871","tid":2224398,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:43:58.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\"><strong>開始前，請知道自己嘅網絡安全知識有幾多，如果係新手嘅話，呢度未必適合你，你可以去上周庭嘅網絡安全bb班先。</strong></span></span> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V7u9LxjJDtg&amp;ab_channel=%E5%91%A8%E5%BA%AD%E3%83%81%E3%83%A3%E3%83%B3%E3%83%8D%E3%83%AB \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DV7u9LxjJDtg%26ab_channel%3D%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E3%2583%2581%25E3%2583%25A3%25E3%2583%25B3%25E3%2583%258D%25E3%2583%25AB%20&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyh5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=7f86d5f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V7u9LxjJDtg&amp;ab_channel=%E5%91%A8%E5%BA%AD%E3%83%81%E3%83%A3%E3%83%B3%E3%83%8D%E3%83%AB </a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>呢個攻略係純教學，較少解釋術語同原理 。如果你唔明，可以上網search如果有嘅自己上網search了解更多。 </strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>網絡安全（Cyber Security）</strong>分為兩大類，分別係<span class=\"red\"><strong>反電子鑑證(Anti-forensics)</strong></span>以及<span class=\"red\"><strong>反電子追蹤(Anti-tracking) </strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n進行呢兩種措施前，硬件亦有要求，就係要<strong>鬼機鬼卡</strong>。<br />\n<strong>手機要求：</strong><br />\na) 最好<span class=\"blue\">新機同較新型號</span>(新機較難被破解，建議買pixel／iphone，而其他encrypted phone喺香港好難買到)，買嘅時候都唔好check location／開wifi connection) 。二手機就盡量揀非本地用過嘅<br />\nb) 有一定電子安全知識嘅 可選<span class=\"blue\">linux/android系統電話</span>，因為更高嘅私隱調整自由度<br />\n<br />\n<strong>太空卡：</strong>無特別要求，只要非大陸供應商就ok<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">反鑑證(Anti-forensic)</span></span><br />\n電話鑑證大致上分為三種方法:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yu5gZoo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYu5gZoo.png&h=d7e76fc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三個方法當中，logical acquisition係最容易，消耗時間較短。相反如果鑑證人員需要拎最全面嘅數據，可能就要利用physical acqu。 不過相當耗時間且有機會破壞原有檔案 。<br />\n<br />\n最原始亦能保護數據嘅最好鑑證方法係成功破解密碼（所以<span class=\"blue\">密碼係最重要嘅保壘之一</span>）。現時知名鑑證儀器供應商有<strong><span class=\"blue\">Cellebrite</span></strong>同<strong><span class=\"blue\">Grayshift</span></strong>。<br />\n<strong>要點防止數據洩露嘅教學如下</strong>：<br />\n<strong>1. 基本手機設定</strong><br />\n- 新增<span class=\"red\">sim lock</span>同數據<span class=\"red\">資料加密(data encryption)</span>。<br />\n- 取消所有app位置(location)權限，Apps有得<span class=\"red\">2FA/2SV</span>嘅就開。<br />\n- disable 所有icloud/Google backup，location，bluetooth<br />\n- disable所有google app，andriod改用<span class=\"blue\">F-driod下載FOSS軟件</span>，就算需要用到google play／App store都用假帳下載<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 備份(Backup)</strong><br />\n推薦用<strong><span class=\"red\">外置儲存器（eg. usb）&gt;雲端儲存</span></strong><br />\n外置儲存器: <span class=\"blue\">SecureDrive</span><span class=\"blue\">(軍用級加密硬碟</span>，相當貴) ，或者普通usb + software加密（e.g. <span class=\"blue\">symantec endpoint encryption, TrueCrypt</span>）<br />\n棄用Google Drive, 改用Nextcloud / TeamDrive<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>3. 文件加密(File encryption) &amp; 文件匿藏法(File Concealment)</strong></span><br />\n電腦: <span class=\"blue\">Veracrypt</span>同<span class=\"blue\">AES crypt</span>可以創建<strong>虛擬加密磁盤文件</strong>，利用演算法增加密碼複雜性破解難度。呢個方法適合儲存一啲重要並且要keep住嘅資料。<br />\nveracrypt仲有得創建<span class=\"blue\">隱藏式磁盤文件</span>。<br />\n中文教學：<a href=\"https://izaka.tw/2015-3-8-226/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fizaka.tw%2F2015-3-8-226%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyh5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=ebb532ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://izaka.tw/2015-3-8-226/</a><br />\nEnglish version: <a href=\"https://proprivacy.com/privacy-service/guides/veracrypt-how-to-basics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fproprivacy.com%2Fprivacy-service%2Fguides%2Fveracrypt-how-to-basics&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyh5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=426e60d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://proprivacy.com/privacy-service/guides/veracrypt-how-to-basics</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Andriod:</strong>下載<span class=\"blue\"><strong>SSE</strong></span>，將重要檔案加密隱藏。<span class=\"blue\">去app --&gt; 禁File/Dir Encryptor --&gt;揀檔案 --&gt;Encrypt file --&gt;set密碼</span>。需要用時就解密（decrypt）。<br />\n<strong>iOS</strong>: 用<span class=\"blue\">securesafe／cryptomator</span>（收費），但iphone本身有內置file加密，所以並唔大問題。<br />\n<br />\n其他方法例如:data steganography(數據隱寫術) ，但個人認為以上兩種已經足夠，所以唔晒篇幅寫。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">4. 數據刪除(data wipe) / 數據覆寫(data overwriting)</span></strong><br />\n真正<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>永久刪除資料</strong></span>方法係多次覆寫原有數據儲存空間。定期要<span class=\"blue\">清除cache+做overwriting</span>。<br />\n<strong>Apps</strong>： <span class=\"blue\">ishredder</span> (Andriod版免費，有<strong>軍用級數據銷毀</strong>選擇)<br />\n<em>ps: Protectstar 有各種反間諜安全程式提供（部分需要收費) 。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.protectstar.com/en/for-android\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.protectstar.com%2Fen%2Ffor-android&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyh5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=2e1b689a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.protectstar.com/en/for-android</a></em><br />\n<br />\n<strong>5. 鍵盤輸入</strong><br />\n電話會<span class=\"blue\">儲存文字輸入歷史</span>，入侵者可以借呢個漏洞去盜取密碼等重要資訊。清除方法<br />\n<strong>Andriod:</strong> 去設定--&gt;一般管理--&gt;語言及輸入--&gt;螢幕鍵盤，揀用緊嘅鍵盤--&gt;重置為預設設定&amp;取消personalized serivce<br />\n<strong>iOS: </strong>去設定--&gt;一般重設--&gt;重設鍵盤辭典<br />\n或者簡單啲就去設定--&gt;應用程式--&gt;揀第三方鍵盤App，然後<span class=\"blue\">clear data&amp;cache</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://windowsreport.com/anti-keylogger-software/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwindowsreport.com%2Fanti-keylogger-software%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyh5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=7e6abab9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://windowsreport.com/anti-keylogger-software/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>6. Metadata</strong><br />\n好多電話相機相片會有metadata，可能<span class=\"blue\">透露相片拍攝位址同手機硬件資料</span>，所以係share出去嘅時候要remove咗先。 <br />\n<strong>Andriod</strong>:下載<span class=\"blue\">Scrambled Exif</span>，喺share相之前揀呢個先（禁落相share就有呢個選擇）<br />\n<strong>iOS</strong>: Metapho<strong><br />\n電腦</strong>：除咗<span class=\"blue\">去terminal改metadata</span>，可以去 <a href=\"https://www.verexif.com/en/改。如果想匿名上載文件，可以下載\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.verexif.com%2Fen%2F%E6%94%B9%E3%80%82%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E6%83%B3%E5%8C%BF%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%8A%E8%BC%89%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E8%BC%89&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyh5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=60ffcd37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.verexif.com/en/改。如果想匿名上載文件，可以下載</a><span class=\"blue\">onionshare</span>透過tor去share<br />\n<br />\n另一個做法<strong>係screenshot將相先send（電話／電腦）</strong><br />\n<br />\n至於平時用開嘅文件editor（eg microsoft word）Metadata，去返word<span class=\"blue\">揀Review--&gt;Protect--&gt;Protect document--&gt;揀&quot;remove personal info from this file on save&quot;同set密碼</span><br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>pdf清除metadata方法</strong>：去pdf properties改。但簡單起見，直接去<a href=\"https://www.pdfyeah.com/remove-pdf-metadata/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pdfyeah.com%2Fremove-pdf-metadata%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyh5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=47fef0e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pdfyeah.com/remove-pdf-metadata/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T16:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d638e5474eb95350e32b1016aaeb8c81a19c5bb5","tid":2224398,"uid":142712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T17:16:44.000Z","msg":"買部鬼機簡單得多"},{"pid":"0202ea15795b83c78acebd19a3a915db2121c143","tid":2224398,"uid":310817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T17:20:01.000Z","msg":"push,等你出新文章"},{"pid":"99d9fca11c935eb34f7eedf9578f3aa09ec7954d","tid":2224398,"uid":169207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T17:58:59.000Z","msg":"Push"}],"pinned":{"pid":"37418d76321e7c43096819a4343a3becf7a053fa","tid":2224398,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T13:18:29.000Z","msg":"暫時唔po了 一長文回覆就出問題po唔到..."}}